WEBVTT

01:34.240 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:38.320 --> 01:44.080
AT OFFICER CHEN'S HOME

01:46.320 --> 01:47.880
SANG YAN
WHERE ARE YOU? WHERE ARE YOU?

01:47.960 --> 01:48.960
CALL ME BACK WHEN YOU SEE THIS

01:49.040 --> 01:50.120
DID YOU GET YOUR ADMISSION LETTER?

01:50.200 --> 01:51.280
TEXT ME BACK
I'M COMING TO FIND YOU

01:56.040 --> 01:57.040
You know what?

01:57.120 --> 01:59.200
I'm going to marry my dream guy!

01:59.280 --> 02:00.960
You think dream guys are that easy to get?

02:01.040 --> 02:02.520
He'll have you wrapped around his finger.

02:02.600 --> 02:05.920
- No, I'll have him wrapped around mine!
- Yifan, we're about to eat.

02:06.000 --> 02:08.360
I want to go out for a bit
and meet a friend.

02:08.440 --> 02:10.280
- Going out?
- Do you want me to go with you?

02:11.280 --> 02:12.480
- No, thanks.
- It's raining outside.

02:13.920 --> 02:15.000
It's fine.

02:15.080 --> 02:17.120
Alright, fine. Have fun.

02:18.360 --> 02:19.840
- I'll be back soon.
- Okay.

02:21.000 --> 02:22.920
- Thanks.
- Enjoy yourself.

03:03.760 --> 03:06.880
I got into Nanwu University!

03:13.000 --> 03:13.880
What's with that reaction?

03:14.760 --> 03:15.800
Bro, think about it…

03:15.880 --> 03:17.440
We can still be classmates!

03:17.520 --> 03:19.360
Plus, you know how bad my grades were.

03:19.440 --> 03:21.000
When I got into Nanwu University,

03:21.080 --> 03:22.920
my grandparents were over the moon.

03:23.440 --> 03:25.240
Back when you said
you were aiming for Nanwu University,

03:25.320 --> 03:27.480
I was like, "How good can it be

03:27.560 --> 03:29.320
that you'd go all out for it?"

03:29.400 --> 03:30.440
But I also said,

03:30.520 --> 03:32.520
"Wherever you apply, I'll apply."

03:32.600 --> 03:34.160
I may not have many strengths,

03:34.240 --> 03:35.960
but one thing's for sure, I keep my word.

03:48.680 --> 03:49.800
3,975 DAYS

03:50.600 --> 03:52.600
Because she just did this…

03:52.680 --> 03:54.520
Did you break it?

03:54.600 --> 03:55.600
Can you remember the moves?

03:55.680 --> 03:57.080
- It's fine.
- Like this…

03:57.160 --> 03:58.040
Just a little…

03:59.800 --> 04:01.840
What do you want?
Do you want to apply more lipstick?

04:01.920 --> 04:04.040
- That's enough.
- I'll do it myself.

04:05.240 --> 04:06.400
Left foot.

04:07.240 --> 04:08.400
Sen…

04:08.480 --> 04:09.560
Right foot.

04:10.760 --> 04:12.160
Rise. Left foot.

04:12.240 --> 04:14.680
Everyone should…

04:15.920 --> 04:17.079
Again, left foot.

04:17.880 --> 04:18.800
Right foot.

04:19.320 --> 04:20.920
Alright, drop.

04:21.000 --> 04:22.000
DO NOT OPEN THE DOOR

04:23.800 --> 04:24.640
Hello? Yes.

04:24.720 --> 04:26.960
There's an issue with the music file.
You need to check it.

04:27.040 --> 04:28.920
Alright, I'm on my way.

04:37.280 --> 04:38.760
Next up is Dian's group.

04:38.840 --> 04:40.560
- Have you seen Sang Yan?
- Not yet.

04:40.640 --> 04:42.680
But he said he's at the airport.
He should be here soon.

04:43.280 --> 04:45.560
- I'll go wait inside then.
- Okay.

04:47.080 --> 04:48.920
- Don't forget to record it.
- Got it.

04:56.520 --> 04:57.760
Are you ready?

05:00.520 --> 05:02.520
Don't be nervous when you're on stage.

05:04.160 --> 05:05.440
You got this!

05:09.600 --> 05:11.920
Wendy, I'll go check the music file
at the front desk.

05:12.000 --> 05:13.360
They said there's an issue.

05:13.440 --> 05:14.560
I'll go with you.

05:14.640 --> 05:15.600
Alright.

05:25.800 --> 05:26.920
Come on.

05:27.000 --> 05:30.320
Listen to me. Now, everyone,
sit down where you are.

05:35.120 --> 05:36.200
Quick.

05:37.120 --> 05:38.000
We've been practicing

05:38.080 --> 05:39.840
- this dance for a long time, haven't we?
- Yes.

05:39.920 --> 05:42.520
I see all the effort you've put in.

05:42.600 --> 05:43.840
Later on,

05:43.920 --> 05:46.680
even if the music doesn't play,
I know you've got the rhythm

05:46.760 --> 05:47.680
deep in your hearts.

05:47.760 --> 05:48.680
- Right?
- Right.

05:49.600 --> 05:52.120
Now, close your eyes with me.

05:53.920 --> 05:55.200
Breathe in.

05:56.480 --> 05:57.320
And out.

05:57.400 --> 05:59.640
Think back

05:59.720 --> 06:01.880
to the happiest moment when we danced.

06:02.640 --> 06:04.120
Once we're on stage,

06:04.200 --> 06:07.360
just enjoy the moment
and feel the joy. Alright?

06:07.440 --> 06:10.200
- Alright.
- Great. Stand up now.

06:13.440 --> 06:14.560
Wendy,

06:15.400 --> 06:16.440
they confirmed it.

06:17.160 --> 06:18.520
The music file is corrupted.

06:21.120 --> 06:22.240
It's okay.

06:22.840 --> 06:25.040
When you're on stage, I'll be right here.

06:25.120 --> 06:26.720
Listen, even without music,

06:26.800 --> 06:27.640
we can still dance beautifully.

06:27.720 --> 06:29.360
- Right?
- Right!

06:29.440 --> 06:31.240
We're the best. Aren't we?

06:31.320 --> 06:32.160
Yes!

06:32.240 --> 06:33.640
We can do this, right?

06:33.720 --> 06:34.880
- Yes!
- Let's go for it!

06:34.960 --> 06:36.440
Alright!

06:36.520 --> 06:38.200
We've prepared for so long.
We have to go on.

06:38.280 --> 06:39.120
Yes!

06:39.640 --> 06:42.360
Let's shout it out. Let's do this!

06:42.440 --> 06:44.600
Let's do this!

06:48.880 --> 06:50.760
Bro, do you know what time it is now?

06:50.840 --> 06:52.240
Why are you here so late?

06:52.760 --> 06:53.920
Flight delay.

06:55.600 --> 06:57.480
I'll leave this to you.
She's waiting for you.

06:59.160 --> 07:00.360
Thanks!

07:05.240 --> 07:08.360
For the next performance,
we're having some music issues.

07:08.440 --> 07:10.680
But they said
after practicing for so long,

07:10.760 --> 07:12.480
they have to go on stage, no matter what.

07:12.560 --> 07:14.800
Let's give them
a big round of encouragement!

07:14.880 --> 07:17.920
Here come the kids
from Sunshine Dance Studio!

07:34.520 --> 07:36.880
SEAT

07:36.960 --> 07:38.920
Excuse me.
Where is the children's performance?

07:39.000 --> 07:40.480
Inside. They've already started.

07:41.320 --> 07:42.480
Thank you.

08:20.640 --> 08:22.640
Contestant No. 7, Wen Yifan.

08:58.000 --> 08:59.920
- Excuse me. Coming through.
- Alright.

09:27.560 --> 09:30.000
I feel like the guy
next to me is Sang Yan.

09:32.360 --> 09:33.520
Probably is.

09:35.920 --> 09:37.080
He's pretty handsome.

09:38.680 --> 09:39.600
Yeah.

09:40.360 --> 09:41.480
More than you.

09:42.400 --> 09:43.360
I think so, too.

10:15.760 --> 10:16.640
That was amazing!

10:20.360 --> 10:21.200
Let's go.

10:21.280 --> 10:22.400
Go.

10:22.480 --> 10:23.800
Take care.

10:26.200 --> 10:28.480
You danced so well today!

10:28.560 --> 10:30.080
Why were you so amazing today?

10:30.160 --> 10:31.480
Everyone was amazing today!

10:31.560 --> 10:32.640
Yeah.

10:34.880 --> 10:36.000
Wen Yifan.

11:07.680 --> 11:09.440
What happened to your foot?

11:13.840 --> 11:16.680
I twisted it while dancing with the kids.

11:21.880 --> 11:22.840
You just got off the plane?

11:25.680 --> 11:26.840
I didn't want to miss your performance.

11:29.120 --> 11:29.960
Where's Qiao and the others?

11:31.840 --> 11:32.800
They said

11:32.880 --> 11:35.520
they wanted to see the night view,
so they left.

11:46.440 --> 11:48.800
Are you coming to our celebration later?

11:51.000 --> 11:51.920
Sure.

11:54.840 --> 11:57.600
The kids didn't win any awards today,

11:58.320 --> 12:00.760
but they were happier
than if they had won first place.

12:02.080 --> 12:03.320
Me, too.

12:07.120 --> 12:08.080
Seeing you…

12:10.880 --> 12:12.480
makes me happier than anything else.

13:24.440 --> 13:25.560
After coming here,

13:25.640 --> 13:28.600
I checked and knew
that I was eligible to apply for school.

13:28.680 --> 13:30.840
So, I was thinking
maybe I should give it a try.

13:33.120 --> 13:34.080
Do you really want
to go back to school that much?

13:35.360 --> 13:36.440
Not exactly.

13:37.760 --> 13:39.280
I just want to be better.

13:41.000 --> 13:42.280
You're already more than enough.

13:43.720 --> 13:44.960
Only then would I deserve you.

13:46.360 --> 13:48.240
Are you flattering me in a roundabout way?

13:53.960 --> 13:55.160
It was because of him.

13:56.760 --> 13:58.480
He made me feel

14:00.120 --> 14:01.920
like I didn't deserve good things,

14:03.280 --> 14:04.880
and like he could take it all away
at any moment.

14:06.960 --> 14:09.080
It's his fault.
You don't have to carry this alone.

14:09.880 --> 14:11.200
Understand?

14:14.560 --> 14:15.880
You disappearing without a word

14:17.080 --> 14:18.480
was what really destroyed my world.

14:19.520 --> 14:20.480
Understand?

14:27.320 --> 14:28.320
I love you.

14:29.800 --> 14:30.720
So much.

14:44.080 --> 14:45.240
Looks like it's going to rain.

14:45.880 --> 14:46.960
Should we buy an umbrella?

14:52.880 --> 14:54.760
I should've given you
my umbrella that day.

14:56.800 --> 14:57.920
What day?

15:00.720 --> 15:02.720
The day college admission results
came out.

15:03.600 --> 15:05.040
When you came to Beiyu to see me.

15:07.560 --> 15:09.160
That day, it rained?

15:11.920 --> 15:14.280
So what if I got wet? Why apologize?

15:14.360 --> 15:16.120
I'm a grown man.
Getting rained on is no big deal.

15:16.200 --> 15:17.440
I'm not that fragile.

15:18.920 --> 15:22.160
Stop treating your boyfriend
like a delicate flower.

15:24.920 --> 15:26.040
What are you laughing at?

15:34.760 --> 15:37.320
This hotel I booked for you

15:37.400 --> 15:38.440
isn't that great.

15:39.880 --> 15:42.080
It's fine. It has a unique charm.

15:46.760 --> 15:49.680
I'll go check if they have two rooms.

15:51.400 --> 15:52.880
I only booked one.

15:57.440 --> 15:59.120
So, are you planning

15:59.200 --> 16:00.280
to go back home?

16:05.000 --> 16:06.200
It has two beds.

16:14.120 --> 16:16.240
Sit tight. I'll check us in.

16:16.840 --> 16:17.800
Wait here.

16:20.480 --> 16:21.440
- Hello.
- How can I help you?

16:21.520 --> 16:22.640
I have a reservation.

16:38.880 --> 16:39.840
Come here.

16:45.480 --> 16:46.480
Sit.

16:58.080 --> 16:59.960
When did you buy the medicine?

17:00.040 --> 17:00.920
Just now.

17:03.440 --> 17:04.560
While you were showering.

17:06.040 --> 17:06.920
Does it hurt?

17:18.640 --> 17:20.040
This leg injury

17:20.119 --> 17:22.680
was got back in Beiyu.

17:28.040 --> 17:30.360
Back then, I was trying
to escape from Che Xingde,

17:30.440 --> 17:32.640
the man who called himself my Uncle Che.

17:33.400 --> 17:35.280
I jumped from the second floor.

17:35.360 --> 17:36.880
That's when I got hurt.

17:38.440 --> 17:41.760
Dancing with the kids
made the old injury flare up again.

17:47.880 --> 17:51.120
The first time I saw him in Nanwu
was one night

17:51.200 --> 17:53.360
when I was covering a car accident.

17:53.440 --> 17:54.880
He was involved.

17:56.320 --> 17:58.520
But nothing happened that night.

18:00.400 --> 18:03.240
The next time I saw him
was when we were at Overtime together.

18:04.960 --> 18:08.520
And then later, he applied to be
a security guard at my workplace.

18:14.840 --> 18:16.720
I didn't tell you the truth back then.

18:18.480 --> 18:21.440
After moving to Beiyu,
Che Xingde lived with us.

18:22.720 --> 18:24.360
He did a lot for my Uncle Wen's family,

18:24.440 --> 18:26.760
so no one dared
to say anything against him.

18:27.960 --> 18:29.280
No one dared to cross him.

18:33.200 --> 18:34.360
It was him.

18:43.760 --> 18:45.920
He kept… harassing me.

18:57.600 --> 18:58.760
Wen Shuangjiang…

19:00.280 --> 19:01.400
If you don't want to talk about it, don't.

19:04.120 --> 19:05.320
It's not that I don't want to.

19:09.360 --> 19:11.880
One night, he broke into my room.

19:14.320 --> 19:15.760
I fought back as hard as I could.

19:17.040 --> 19:19.680
My Uncle Wen's family
usually didn't get back from selling food

19:19.760 --> 19:21.200
until 3 a.m.

19:23.840 --> 19:25.400
But that night, it rained.

19:26.560 --> 19:28.320
So, they came home early.

19:33.120 --> 19:35.000
Luckily, they came home early.

19:48.600 --> 19:50.680
At that time, I didn't know what to do.

19:53.480 --> 19:54.320
No one helped me.

20:21.920 --> 20:24.520
Not a single person stood by my side.

20:27.720 --> 20:29.400
Not even my mom.

20:45.680 --> 20:47.560
So, I didn't think about anything else.

20:47.640 --> 20:48.840
I just wanted

20:48.920 --> 20:50.920
to get far away from Nanwu and Beiyu.

20:52.200 --> 20:54.000
I wanted to go somewhere far, far away.

20:59.400 --> 21:01.800
I'm sorry. I should've told you all this.

21:06.600 --> 21:09.080
But at first,
I really did apply to Nanwu University.

21:10.080 --> 21:11.800
I wanted to go to college with you.

21:17.800 --> 21:18.640
I wasn't lying.

21:22.880 --> 21:24.320
I'm sorry, Sang Yan.

21:28.360 --> 21:30.640
I said a lot of things that hurt you.

21:32.960 --> 21:34.680
But that's not what I really meant.

21:43.560 --> 21:44.720
It's okay.

21:49.000 --> 21:50.200
If there's something
you wanted to say back then,

21:52.440 --> 21:53.360
say it now.

21:55.000 --> 21:56.480
I just felt like…

21:57.400 --> 21:58.960
I was the one who changed my application.

22:00.200 --> 22:01.600
I was the one who messed up.

22:02.600 --> 22:04.480
And Nanwu is really far from Yihe.

22:06.160 --> 22:09.080
I didn't want you running around
all the time like you did in high school.

22:10.840 --> 22:11.920
It was too much for you.

22:16.320 --> 22:17.360
Anything else?

22:19.480 --> 22:21.200
I never made any promises to anyone.

22:25.680 --> 22:26.920
Only to you.

22:31.280 --> 22:32.400
I know.

22:34.200 --> 22:37.080
GOAL: NANWU UNIVERSITY!

22:46.600 --> 22:48.040
I don't deserve you.

23:02.080 --> 23:03.520
Wen Shuangjiang.

23:05.800 --> 23:07.080
Take that back.

23:08.320 --> 23:10.040
Do you know why I never dated
anyone all these years?

23:13.840 --> 23:15.640
Because I only wanted the best.

23:18.720 --> 23:19.920
Understand?

23:31.760 --> 23:33.400
I never saw you as a backup.

23:37.560 --> 23:38.680
All these years,

23:39.280 --> 23:41.480
there was never anyone else. Only you.

23:45.200 --> 23:46.200
I'm sorry, Sang Yan.

23:46.280 --> 23:48.040
I broke our promise.

23:52.600 --> 23:54.120
Stop saying sorry.

23:56.920 --> 23:57.960
I forgive you.

23:59.480 --> 24:01.200
So, from now on, no more apologies.

24:01.840 --> 24:02.840
Okay?

24:05.880 --> 24:08.240
Back then, Che Xingde told me…

24:09.960 --> 24:12.600
it was shameful and humiliating.

24:14.720 --> 24:18.040
My relatives said the same.
They told me not to report it.

24:18.840 --> 24:20.920
They said it would ruin my reputation.

24:21.800 --> 24:23.760
That's why I didn't want you to know.

24:27.120 --> 24:29.280
If only I had told you back then.

24:33.440 --> 24:34.760
Wen Shuangjiang.

24:36.760 --> 24:39.280
Don't listen to that villain's nonsense.

24:45.000 --> 24:45.840
Listen to me.

24:47.320 --> 24:48.840
There is nothing shameful
or humiliating about this.

24:49.520 --> 24:50.720
Understand?

24:51.960 --> 24:54.880
You did nothing wrong.
You did the right thing.

24:55.800 --> 24:57.920
You protected yourself. You were brave.

25:00.520 --> 25:03.080
You should be standing tall,
fearless, in the sunlight.

25:05.160 --> 25:07.080
That villain is the one
who belongs to the gutter.

25:08.960 --> 25:09.920
Got it?

25:47.000 --> 25:48.160
Thank you.

25:52.360 --> 25:53.640
You protected my Jiang.

26:08.840 --> 26:10.080
Also…

26:12.280 --> 26:13.840
saying all this now

26:14.360 --> 26:15.560
isn't late at all.

26:16.600 --> 26:18.800
If you had told me this back then,

26:19.720 --> 26:21.480
maybe I wouldn't have wanted to date.

26:22.080 --> 26:24.160
Even if you chased me,
I wouldn't have said yes.

26:30.840 --> 26:33.960
But back then,
you were the one chasing me first.

26:41.720 --> 26:43.000
Didn't you like me, too?

26:46.600 --> 26:49.040
If you like me, chase me properly.

26:49.120 --> 26:50.840
Look at you.

26:51.600 --> 26:53.760
Liking someone but waiting for them
to make the first move.

26:53.840 --> 26:54.880
That much pride?

26:55.960 --> 26:57.400
I just didn't know how to chase someone.

26:58.000 --> 26:59.320
And you think I did?

27:01.240 --> 27:02.760
You seem pretty experienced.

27:05.080 --> 27:07.920
You say you're easygoing,

27:08.000 --> 27:09.680
but sometimes, you're really annoying.

27:16.640 --> 27:18.720
- What?
- Let me touch you.

27:24.360 --> 27:25.520
What's this?

27:26.880 --> 27:28.440
I fell before.

27:28.520 --> 27:29.920
Where did you get hurt?

27:30.000 --> 27:31.320
I just tripped. That's all.

27:32.240 --> 27:34.480
- How did it happen?
- It's nothing. It's healed.

27:35.000 --> 27:36.040
This doesn't look healed at all.

27:36.120 --> 27:38.920
How is this "nothing"?
How did you get this?

28:12.240 --> 28:13.240
Why did you stop?

28:18.800 --> 28:19.920
I see.

28:22.520 --> 28:26.120
So, that's why you went out of your way
to book only one room

28:29.520 --> 28:33.840
and even tried to cover it up
by choosing a twin-bed room.

28:36.520 --> 28:38.640
Fine, I'll go take a shower.

28:39.160 --> 28:40.280
Then…

28:41.480 --> 28:42.960
should I wait for you?

28:44.680 --> 28:45.720
What else?

28:48.000 --> 28:51.120
Or… do you want to skip that
and view my body now? Here?

28:52.680 --> 28:53.680
Or here?

28:54.640 --> 28:55.720
Or maybe here?

30:07.000 --> 30:09.240
Are they all your students?

30:11.080 --> 30:13.320
- Do you like this job?
- I do.

30:13.400 --> 30:14.240
- Here you are.
- Yesterday,

30:14.320 --> 30:16.480
the music file crashed
right before they went on stage,

30:16.560 --> 30:18.480
but they still went out and performed.

30:19.000 --> 30:20.040
I was really moved.

30:21.880 --> 30:23.840
And when they danced,

30:23.920 --> 30:25.640
their eyes sparkled.

30:25.720 --> 30:28.920
That pure, simple joy
reminded me of so many things.

30:29.680 --> 30:31.760
Honestly, rather than me
teaching them to dance,

30:32.360 --> 30:34.720
it feels like they taught me so much more.

30:38.520 --> 30:39.480
Eat up!

30:39.560 --> 30:41.120
Wendy, where are you going?

30:45.280 --> 30:46.120
I'm going home.

30:46.200 --> 30:48.480
Will you come back and play with us?

30:48.560 --> 30:49.880
Of course!

30:49.960 --> 30:51.680
Whenever I have time, I'll come visit you.

30:54.160 --> 30:56.680
Listen up! I'm leaving for now.

30:57.200 --> 30:59.560
But while I'm gone, keep practicing hard.

30:59.640 --> 31:01.360
I'll come back to check on you, alright?

31:01.440 --> 31:02.680
Alright!

31:04.720 --> 31:06.640
Sorry. I had to leave so suddenly.

31:07.560 --> 31:08.760
It's fine.

31:08.840 --> 31:10.920
Didn't we agree on this before?
You'd stay until your course was done.

31:11.000 --> 31:12.720
And now, it's about that time.

31:12.800 --> 31:15.320
I should be thanking you
for stepping in just in time.

31:16.520 --> 31:19.560
So, he's the one
you've been thinking about nonstop?

31:19.640 --> 31:20.720
Who? Me?

31:22.240 --> 31:24.840
When we're free, we'll come visit you.

31:24.920 --> 31:26.240
- Sure.
- Alright, drop by anytime.

31:26.320 --> 31:28.400
Can we take a picture with Wendy?

31:29.760 --> 31:31.000
Why don't we take a big group photo first?

31:31.080 --> 31:31.920
Let's take a group picture!

31:32.000 --> 31:33.800
Then we'll take turns
for individual shots, alright?

31:33.880 --> 31:36.280
- Okay!
- Here, you handle the camera.

31:36.360 --> 31:38.600
One, two, three!

31:38.680 --> 31:40.400
Yeah!

31:41.320 --> 31:42.960
So pretty.

31:43.480 --> 31:44.720
You look so cute.

31:45.320 --> 31:46.840
What? Do you want one, too?

31:47.600 --> 31:48.720
You're smiling so much.

31:48.800 --> 31:49.840
Three, two, one!

31:50.880 --> 31:51.960
Alright.

32:29.680 --> 32:32.280
I guess you don't like this place, do you?

32:37.600 --> 32:39.000
How do you know?

32:39.600 --> 32:40.760
You barely have any luggage.

32:40.840 --> 32:42.120
That tells me you
never planned on staying long.

32:46.160 --> 32:48.400
I just want to be where you are.

32:51.520 --> 32:52.560
I'll help you pack.

33:26.200 --> 33:31.920
NANWU

33:42.320 --> 33:43.800
I really admire you.

33:43.880 --> 33:45.200
You have the courage
to leave everything behind,

33:45.280 --> 33:46.800
to disappear from the world.

33:47.400 --> 33:49.600
What made you change your mind?

33:49.680 --> 33:51.280
It was him.

33:51.920 --> 33:53.880
He gave me a lot of courage.

33:53.960 --> 33:56.080
He made me realize

33:56.720 --> 33:58.520
that not everything can be solved
by hiding in the shadows.

33:59.400 --> 34:02.360
You know,
maybe we can't live for love alone,

34:02.440 --> 34:04.600
but love really does
give us so much courage.

34:05.520 --> 34:07.200
That's how I felt when I had my child.

34:07.920 --> 34:09.040
The treatment is all done.

34:09.120 --> 34:10.440
You both can rest a little longer.

34:10.520 --> 34:11.800
If you need anything,
just call us anytime.

34:11.880 --> 34:12.960
Thank you.

34:22.920 --> 34:24.480
I feel like my looks

34:24.560 --> 34:25.800
just leveled up again.

34:25.880 --> 34:27.239
By lots of levels.

34:27.960 --> 34:30.800
But I am still several levels below you.

34:31.920 --> 34:34.400
We deserve all the good things in life.
So, we have to take care of ourselves.

34:36.840 --> 34:37.880
By the way,

34:37.960 --> 34:39.120
will you go back to the TV station?

34:40.639 --> 34:43.480
I've been gone for so long.

34:43.560 --> 34:46.199
Do you think Ms. Qian and Mr. Gan
would still take me back?

34:46.280 --> 34:48.400
At worst, you'll just
have to pass their test again.

34:52.280 --> 34:55.840
- Have you put on some weight recently?
- Have I?

34:55.920 --> 34:57.800
Of course!

34:57.880 --> 35:01.400
You used to be all skin and bones.
It hurt to lean on you.

35:05.360 --> 35:07.560
Now look at you, all happy and plump.

35:16.840 --> 35:19.200
I met up with Su Tian today.

35:20.400 --> 35:22.520
Seeing her brought back so many memories.

35:24.480 --> 35:25.600
Want to go back to the station?

35:29.120 --> 35:29.960
What do you think?

35:31.240 --> 35:32.480
Do you like this job?

35:34.840 --> 35:36.760
As long as you like it and want to do it,

35:36.840 --> 35:38.920
no matter what it is,
I'll always support you.

35:53.080 --> 35:55.160
You're the most handsome man
I've ever seen.

35:59.640 --> 36:01.560
Shouldn't you be shouting that out loud?

36:04.240 --> 36:05.920
I have the most handsome man.

36:10.480 --> 36:11.360
And you're a fairy.

36:15.600 --> 36:16.520
Want some fruit?

36:16.600 --> 36:17.960
Here, have a cherry.

36:23.960 --> 36:26.000
Have you had
any sleepwalking episodes recently?

36:27.360 --> 36:29.720
Back when you studied in Hong Kong, China,

36:29.800 --> 36:31.840
being in a new environment
must have been stressful.

36:31.920 --> 36:33.640
Did you sleepwalk during that time?

36:33.720 --> 36:35.000
I haven't sleepwalked in a long time.

36:36.520 --> 36:37.920
I think

36:38.000 --> 36:40.280
I'm getting better at handling stress.

36:40.360 --> 36:41.560
From now on,

36:41.640 --> 36:42.920
you just need to keep an eye on it.

36:43.000 --> 36:44.200
No need for further check-ups.

36:45.040 --> 36:47.600
So, can I go back to reporting?

36:47.680 --> 36:49.960
Of course. No one
should have to give up their dreams

36:50.040 --> 36:51.400
just because of sleepwalking.

36:51.480 --> 36:53.440
Besides,
you're in a really stable condition now.

36:54.040 --> 36:56.360
So, go. Give it your all.

36:56.440 --> 36:57.920
Thank you, Doctor.

36:58.000 --> 36:59.280
No problem. Good luck!

37:00.760 --> 37:03.520
NANWU TV STATION

37:05.920 --> 37:07.480
Back when you left,

37:07.560 --> 37:09.600
I couldn't quite understand why.

37:10.760 --> 37:13.120
- Right?
- Of course, she had her reasons.

37:14.520 --> 37:16.360
So, did you find your answer?

37:18.120 --> 37:20.160
This might be a bit direct,

37:20.240 --> 37:21.960
but I'd like to ask you both.

37:22.040 --> 37:23.200
What do you think

37:23.880 --> 37:25.800
is the most important trait
of a journalist?

37:26.880 --> 37:28.760
The drive to pursue the truth.

37:30.720 --> 37:33.200
For me, it's about
keeping the passion alive.

37:34.640 --> 37:36.480
Even though I don't have
the same energy anymore,

37:36.560 --> 37:40.160
whenever I'm the first on the scene,
I can still feel

37:40.240 --> 37:41.440
that rush.

37:43.040 --> 37:44.320
And you? Your turn to answer.

37:45.560 --> 37:47.280
I think journalism can protect people.

37:48.240 --> 37:50.000
When the truth comes to light,

37:50.960 --> 37:53.200
all the ugliness in the dark

37:53.280 --> 37:54.680
can no longer hide.

37:56.520 --> 37:57.880
That's why I want

37:59.240 --> 38:01.120
to grow stronger,

38:01.200 --> 38:03.520
to be braver, so I can fight for the weak.

38:08.760 --> 38:09.920
Yifan,

38:10.000 --> 38:11.880
what's ahead will be even tougher.

38:14.960 --> 38:16.840
I like this version of you.

38:16.920 --> 38:18.080
Welcome back.

38:19.280 --> 38:20.520
Thank you, Ms. Qian.

38:21.640 --> 38:22.680
Good luck!

38:31.080 --> 38:32.320
Hello, landlady?

38:32.400 --> 38:33.560
Miss Wen,

38:33.640 --> 38:37.000
your lease is up next March.

38:37.080 --> 38:38.880
I'm taking the apartment back

38:38.960 --> 38:40.440
as a wedding home for my daughter.

38:40.520 --> 38:42.000
I want to let you know in advance,

38:42.080 --> 38:44.080
so you have time to find a new place.

38:44.600 --> 38:46.080
Got it.

38:47.080 --> 38:49.160
- Congratulations.
- Thank you.

38:54.400 --> 38:56.240
I've been living here with Sang Yan

38:56.320 --> 38:57.680
for over two years now.

39:12.120 --> 39:13.000
Hello? Ms. Qian?

39:13.080 --> 39:14.880
Yifan, are you at the station right now?

39:15.480 --> 39:17.520
- Yeah.
- What about Fu Zhuang?

39:17.600 --> 39:18.560
He's right here.

39:18.640 --> 39:19.480
You two, come down quickly.

39:19.560 --> 39:21.320
We need to head to Beiyu.

39:23.000 --> 39:24.280
Understood.

39:25.480 --> 39:27.640
Ms. Qian said we're going on a trip.
Pack the stuff.

39:27.720 --> 39:29.000
- Right now?
- Yes.

39:35.120 --> 39:38.000
We just got a lead for a news report.

39:38.760 --> 39:41.040
It's about a high school girl
who went missing in Beiyu

39:41.120 --> 39:42.080
a few years ago.

39:42.680 --> 39:43.960
Recently, a woman took a recording

39:44.040 --> 39:46.440
to the police station.

39:46.520 --> 39:48.440
It might be linked to the case.

39:48.520 --> 39:50.960
So now, there's been a major breakthrough.

39:51.040 --> 39:53.320
The police are searching everywhere
for the victim's body.

39:53.920 --> 39:55.760
They've formed a task force

39:55.840 --> 39:57.320
and are going all out
to track down the suspect.

39:58.720 --> 40:00.160
Who's the suspect?

40:00.240 --> 40:03.320
Apparently, his niece-in-law reported him.

40:04.280 --> 40:05.720
What's in the video?

40:05.800 --> 40:07.760
I don't know the details yet.

40:13.520 --> 40:16.480
BEIYU CITY JIANGJIN DISTRICT
PUBLIC SECURITY BUREAU

40:16.560 --> 40:19.880
Hello, sir. We're from Nanwu TV Station.

40:19.960 --> 40:21.920
We spoke to Chief Chen earlier.

40:26.840 --> 40:28.160
Yifan?

40:28.680 --> 40:31.920
- Aunt Chen!
- Yifan, it's really you!

40:32.000 --> 40:33.720
It's been so many years.

40:33.800 --> 40:35.200
You're a reporter now?

40:35.280 --> 40:36.760
What brings you to Beiyu?

40:37.680 --> 40:38.920
We're here on assignment.

40:39.520 --> 40:42.280
Seeing you doing well now,
I'm really happy for you.

40:43.280 --> 40:45.160
How have you guys been?
What about Chen Xi?

40:45.800 --> 40:47.640
She's doing great.
She just got engaged to her boyfriend.

40:48.520 --> 40:49.800
After you left,

40:49.880 --> 40:51.360
she missed you so much.

40:51.440 --> 40:52.960
She used to talk about you all the time.

40:54.120 --> 40:55.400
I saw her posts.

40:55.480 --> 40:57.160
The guy is someone she's always liked.

40:57.800 --> 40:58.960
Congratulations.

40:59.040 --> 41:00.160
Let me know when she gets married.

41:01.040 --> 41:02.240
Of course.

41:21.560 --> 41:26.560
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

41:33.280 --> 41:35.520
You've been standing here forever
and still haven't washed up.

41:36.040 --> 41:37.240
What are you looking at?

41:40.800 --> 41:42.240
There's a hickey here.

41:42.320 --> 41:44.920
I'm worried I won't be able to cover it.
I might not be able to go out.

41:47.240 --> 41:49.080
So, are you

41:50.000 --> 41:51.160
blaming me for this?

41:52.080 --> 41:53.000
Then, what should we do?

41:53.520 --> 41:55.840
What else?
I'll figure out a way to hide it later.

41:57.080 --> 41:59.520
Well, I've already kissed you,
and now you're trying to settle scores?

42:01.240 --> 42:02.360
But you know,

42:03.440 --> 42:04.520
I'm a fair person.

42:05.480 --> 42:06.800
How about this?

42:07.440 --> 42:08.760
You kiss me here, too.

42:09.760 --> 42:11.440
Go to work already!

42:12.080 --> 42:14.480
- Just one kiss.
- Move it!

42:17.400 --> 42:18.480
You're really not going to kiss me?

45:04.240 --> 45:05.280
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

45:05.360 --> 45:06.600
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
